---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About">
  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6 pb-12">
    <h1 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl font-medium mb-12 animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-fill-mode: both;">About</h1>

    <!-- Profile image with warm treatment -->
    <div class="mb-10 animate-fade-in-up stagger-2" style="animation-fill-mode: both;">
      <img
        src="/matthew-strickland.jpg"
        alt="Matthew Strickland"
        class="w-36 h-36 rounded-full object-cover grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-500 ring-4 ring-cream-200 dark:ring-ink-700 hover:ring-sienna-300 dark:hover:ring-sienna-700"
      />
    </div>

    <div class="prose prose-neutral dark:prose-invert animate-fade-in-up stagger-3" style="animation-fill-mode: both;">
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
        I'm Matthew Strickland, a software engineer and engineering leader based in Atlanta, Georgia.
      </p>

      <p>
        Currently, I work on International at <a href="https://chick-fil-a.com">Chick-fil-A</a>,
        building software to support the company's global expansion.
      </p>

      <ul>
        <li>International Markets: <a href="https://www.chick-fil-a.ca">Canada</a> | <a href="https://www.chick-fil-a.pr">Puerto Rico</a> | <a href="https://www.chick-fil-a.com.sg">Singapore</a> | <a href="https://www.chick-fil-a.co.uk">UK</a></li>
        <li>Canada Loyalty & Ordering (<a href="https://apps.apple.com/ca/app/chick-fil-a-canada/id6673919737">iOS</a> & <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.chickfila.international&hl=en_US">Android</a>)</li>
      </ul>

      <p>
        Prior to joining International, I served on our Customer Technology leading teams and building some of the products our customers love:
      </p>

      <ul>
        <li>US Market:
          <ul>
            <li>Chick-fil-A One (<a href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/chick-fil-a/id488818252">iOS</a> & <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.chickfila.cfaflagship">Android</a>)</li>
            <li><a href="https://order.chick-fil-a.com">Web Ordering</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://www.chick-fil-a.com/delivery">Delivery</a></li>
            <li>Drive-Thru Technology</li>
          </ul>
        </li>
      </ul>

      <p>
        Previously, I led the iOS and Web engineering teams at <a href="https://bignerdranch.com">Big Nerd Ranch</a>,
        where I helped organizations launch successful applications. Before that, I worked at
        Vertigo (now Disney Streaming Services), building apps used by millions of people.
      </p>

      <!-- Pull quote -->
      <blockquote class="pull-quote not-prose">
        I love serving others through technology â€” helping teams grow, shipping products that matter,
        and writing about what I learn along the way.
      </blockquote>

      <p>
        If you want to connect, you can find me on <a href="https://x.com/strickland">X</a>,
        <a href="https://github.com/mps">GitHub</a>, or
        <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/mps/">LinkedIn</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
